Sex (001 - 016) (2013 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Darkness-Empire)


Simon Cooke has retired from his own "alternative lifestyle" and returned to the city he'd previously sworn to protect. Now he's just another average citizen -- or is he? The term "adult" has never been so appropriate as it is when it applies to SEX.

Creator owned series by Joe Casey and Piotr Kowalski.
